TITLE: Error Handlers in PHP Silex
DESCRIPTION: Register custom error handlers to handle exceptions and display appropriate error pages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silexphp/Silex/blob/master/doc/usage.rst#2025-04-15_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Symfony\Component\HttpFoundation\Response;
use Symfony\Component\HttpFoundation\Request;

$app->error(function (\Exception $e, Request $request, $code) {
    switch ($code) {
        case 404:
            $message = 'The requested page could not be found.';
            break;
        default:
            $message = 'We are sorry, but something went terribly wrong.';
    }

    return new Response($message);
});
```

