SOURCE: https://github.com/silexphp/Silex/blob/master/doc/providers/security.rst#2025-04-15_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: jinja
CODE:
```
{% if is_granted('ROLE_ADMIN') %}
    <a href="/secured?_switch_user=fabien">Switch to Fabien</a>
{% endif %}
```

LANGUAGE: jinja
CODE:
```
