TITLE: Creating a Feedback Form Email Handler in Silex
DESCRIPTION: Example of a route handler that processes form submissions and sends feedback emails using the SwiftmailerServiceProvider. This demonstrates creating and sending a Swift_Message within a route callback.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silexphp/Silex/blob/master/doc/providers/swiftmailer.rst#2025-04-15_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Symfony\Component\HttpFoundation\Request;

$app->post('/feedback', function (Request $request) use ($app) {
    $message = \Swift_Message::newInstance()
        ->setSubject('[YourSite] Feedback')
        ->setFrom(array('noreply@yoursite.com'))
        ->setTo(array('feedback@yoursite.com'))
        ->setBody($request->get('message'));

    $app['mailer']->send($message);

    return new Response('Thank you for your feedback!', 201);
});
```

