TITLE: Extending Twig Service in Silex
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to modify an existing service after its definition using the extend() method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silexphp/Silex/blob/master/doc/services.rst#2025-04-15_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$app->extend('twig', function($twig, $app) {
    $twig->addGlobal('pi', 3.14);
    $twig->addFilter('levenshtein', new \Twig_Filter_Function('levenshtein'));

    return $twig;
});
```

