TITLE: Extending Form Type Extensions in Silex PHP Application
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to register custom form type extensions by extending the form.type.extensions service in Silex.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silexphp/Silex/blob/master/doc/providers/form.rst#2025-04-15_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$app['your.type.extension.service'] = function ($app) {
    return new YourServiceFormTypeExtension();
};
$app->extend('form.type.extensions', function ($extensions) use ($app) {
    $extensions[] = new YourFormTypeExtension();
    $extensions[] = 'your.type.extension.service';

    return $extensions;
});
```

