TITLE: Configuring Lighttpd for Silex Applications
DESCRIPTION: Lighttpd configuration with URL rewriting for Silex. This sample simple-vhost configuration demonstrates how to route requests to the Silex front controller while preserving access to static assets.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silexphp/Silex/blob/master/doc/web_servers.rst#2025-04-15_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: lighttpd
CODE:
```
server.document-root = "/path/to/app"

url.rewrite-once = (
    # configure some static files
    "^/assets/.+" => "$0",
    "^/favicon\.ico$" => "$0",

    "^(/[^\?]*)(\?.*)?"
 => "/index.php$1$2"
)
```

